WEBVTT

00:00:04.792 --> 00:00:06.434
Hello.

00:00:06.458 --> 00:00:07.726
Hey.

00:00:07.750 --> 00:00:09.184
(Laughter)

00:00:09.208 --> 00:00:10.684
As you just heard,

00:00:10.708 --> 00:00:12.434
my name is D-L Stewart,

00:00:12.458 --> 00:00:16.559
and I'm a faculty member here on campus
at Colorado State University.

00:00:16.583 --> 00:00:20.018
But what's most important
for you to understand about me right now

00:00:20.042 --> 00:00:22.809
is that I identify as both Black

00:00:22.833 --> 00:00:25.292
and as transgender, or trans.

00:00:26.208 --> 00:00:29.917
And yes, I'm going to talk to you today
about how Black trans lives matter.